      <title>英国计划在全球投资峰会上公布财富基金结构</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-11/uk-plans-to-unveil-wealth-fund-structure-at-global-investment-summit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由英国首相基尔·史塔默 (Keir Starmer) 领导的新工党政府希望在秋季举行的投资峰会之前完善英国国家财富基金的架构，并向国际观众展示这一举措。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-11/uk-plans-to-unveil-wealth-fund-structure-at-global-investment-summit</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 16:31:50 GMT</pubDate>
