    <item>
      <title>欧盟国家敦促谴责匈牙利总统奥尔班与普京的会晤</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-11/eu-nations-push-to-censure-hungary-s-orban-over-putin-meeting</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在匈牙利总理维克托·奥尔班（Viktor Orban）以其随心所欲的外交手段访问俄罗斯、乌克兰和美国佛罗里达州的海湖庄园后，六个欧盟国家正在考虑对匈牙利进行谴责。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-11/eu-nations-push-to-censure-hungary-s-orban-over-putin-meeting</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 16:07:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>投资者戴维·萨克斯将在大会上发表演讲，为特朗普助力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-11/investor-david-sacks-to-speak-at-convention-in-boost-for-trump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[风险投资家大卫·萨克斯将在密尔沃基举行的共和党全国代表大会上发表讲话，强调许多知名商界领袖对唐纳德·特朗普与总统乔·拜登重赛的支持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-11/investor-david-sacks-to-speak-at-convention-in-boost-for-trump</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 16:00:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>斯塔默称拜登在白宫会议上“状态良好”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-11/starmer-says-biden-on-good-form-during-white-house-meeting</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国首相基尔·斯塔默 (Keir Starmer) 在华盛顿举行的北约峰会上成为乔·拜登的首席辩护人，他表示，美国总统在周三的白宫会晤中“状态良好”且“了解细节”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-11/starmer-says-biden-on-good-form-during-white-house-meeting</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 16:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
